data.description: Welcome to your own private paradise complete with gorgeous country views and luxurious outdoor living!  Entertain your guests from your vaulted outdoor kitchen that overlooks your inground pool area!  This spacious home features a 20x14 kitchen that has plenty of cabinet space for the chef in your family and also has a full appliance package, island and a pantry.  Other features include a gas fireplace in the family room, a large living room, a split bedroom floor plan, new carpet, fresh paint and a large laundry room.  This home has an oversized garage with 3 bays, a covered deck & front porch, a stylish aluminum fence around the pool and some of the most beautiful country views in the county!  Schedule your viewing today!
